
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home";
}

<!-- Masthead-->
<header class="masthead">
    <div class="container">
        <span><img style="padding-bottom: 2rem; width: 200px; " src="~/Content/assets/img/logos/AxelHarveyLogo2.png" /></span>
        <div class="masthead-subheading">Welcome To Axel Harvey Productions!</div>
        <div class="masthead-heading text-uppercase">Epic Fidelity.  Chill Atmosphere.</div>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-xl text-uppercase" href="#services">Tell Me More</a>
    </div>
</header>
<!-- Services-->
<section class="page-section" id="services">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">Our Services</h2>
            <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Affordable Quality. Chill Atmosphere.</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-volume-up fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                </span>
                <h4 class="my-3">Recording</h4>
                <p class="text-muted">Full Band Tracking, Mixing, Mastering. We work with you where <em>you</em> are at. We use our state of the art studio spaces to let your songs. Our engineers are multi-instrumentalists so we understand context. We are dedicated to help you release your hottest tracks yet. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-microphone-alt fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                </span>
                <h4 class="my-3">Lyric Videos</h4>
                <p class="text-muted">We create professional lyric videos for bands and artists. We'll listen to your track or use one we've rercorded with you and create relevant graphics and animations for the song. Complete with the song's lyrical content.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-camera-retro fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                </span>
                <h4 class="my-3">Video Work</h4>
                <p class="text-muted">A growing demand matched with our growing resources. We now offer small to medium scaled video recordings for your band or a playthrough of one of your songs! Primarily focused on capturing musical performance. We are willing to work with set / costumes / or props. Just ask!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About-->
<section class="page-section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">About</h2>
            <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">"...To practice any art, no matter how well or badly, is a way to make your soul grow. <strong>So do it </strong>..." - Kurt Vonnegut</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="timeline">
            <li>
                <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="~/Content/assets/img/about/about1.jpg" alt="..." /></div>
                <div class="timeline-panel">
                    <div class="timeline-heading">
                        <h4>2009-2019</h4>
                        <h4 class="subheading">A Decade of Gigs</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">All of us have had our humble beginnings in local bands. A lot of us specialized in hard rock and metal. As confidence grew so did our skills. Technology along with us. Today in recording brings different times. Quality can be met through new means and we knew we were on to something.</p></div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-inverted">
                <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="~/Content/assets/img/about/2.jpg" alt="..." /></div>
                <div class="timeline-panel">
                    <div class="timeline-heading">
                        <h4>2020</h4>
                        <h4 class="subheading">An Studio is Born</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">It all started in a few of our bedrooms. Until one day we all pitched in to get a basement remodel and a friend's house. Our journey begins setting up the rooms in dozens of ways. Experimenting. </p></div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="~/Content/assets/img/about/3.jpg" alt="..." /></div>
                <div class="timeline-panel">
                    <div class="timeline-heading">
                        <h4>2021</h4>
                        <h4 class="subheading">Transition to Full Service</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">High Fidelity. Chill Atmosphere. That's our promise. 2020 had brought a lot of reflection for all of us. This also gave musicians the perfect amount of alone time to get new songs written and we have updated to provide <strong>full service</strong>! We're ready, are you?</p></div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-inverted">
                <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="~/Content/assets/img/about/4.jpg" alt="..." /></div>
                <div class="timeline-panel">
                    <div class="timeline-heading">
                        <h4>Book Now for @DateTime.Now.Year!</h4>
                        <h4 class="subheading">Full Service Record / Mixing / Mastering</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted"><a href="@Url.Action("Contact","Home")">Contact us</a> for a quote and when you're ready, come back and create an account to book a time! If you've already created an account, what are you waiting for? Let us make your next new <strong>heavy hit</strong>!</p></div>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li class="timeline-inverted">
                <div class="timeline-image">
                    <h4>
                        <br />
                        @if (Request.IsAuthenticated)
                        {
                        <a style="color:white;" href="@Url.Action("Index","Reservations")">BOOK NOW!</a>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                        <a style="color:white;" href="@Url.Action("Login","Account","Account")">BOOK NOW!</a>   
                        }
                        

                    </h4>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Clients-->
<div class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
                <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto" src="~/Content/assets/img/logos/ibanez.png" alt="Ibanez Logo" /></a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
                <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto" src="~/Content/assets/img/logos/Mackie_Combo_logo-black-outline.png" alt="Mackie Logo" /></a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
                <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto" src="~/Content/assets/img/logos/1280px-Shure_Logo.svg.png" alt="Mackie Logo" /></a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
                <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto" src="~/Content/assets/img/logos/krk.svg" alt="KRK Systems Logo" /></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
